### Tile art attribution

Tile art under `assets/tiles/` comes from the Dungeon Crawl Stone Soup
RLTiles collection, released under CC0 (public domain). See
https://github.com/crawl/tiles for individual tile attribution. CC0 does
not require attribution but the RLTiles project + Linley Henzell / the
DCSS development team deserve mention for decades of roguelike tileset
contributions.

### Prior project (oldproject/)

The `oldproject/` directory contains an earlier DCSS mobile port that is
licensed under GPL v2+ (inherited from DCSS). Its contents are NOT part of
this MIT-licensed project; see `oldproject/README.md` for its separate
distribution terms.
